description:
Stackable, contract grade, all weather chairs perfect for all manner of commercial venues. Quality tested for the most demanding of locations. We offer items in the following category's and more!
  • Metal
  • Plastic
  • Rattan
  • Rope
  • Wooden
  • With shower proof cushions
